## 🔐 Security Architecture

| Layer | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Passwords** | bcrypt hashed — never stored in plain text |
| **Authentication** | JWT tokens, 24h expiry, role embedded in payload |
| **Authorization** | Server-side RBAC middleware on every protected route |
| **University Isolation** | [verify_university_access()](file:///c:/Users/sujit/arvion-ai/backend/app/dependencies.py#30-37) checks user's `university_id` against request |
| **OTP Flow** | 6-digit OTP, email-delivered, 10min expiry, one-time-use |
| **Rate Limiting** | 20 requests/minute per IP (SlowAPI) |
| **Password Reset** | OTP verification required — no direct reset without email access |
| **Secrets** | All secrets in [.env](file:///c:/Users/sujit/arvion-ai/backend/.env) / Cloud Run environment variables — never in code |
| **Super Admin** | Cannot be created through the API. Only via secure [init_super_admin.py](file:///c:/Users/sujit/arvion-ai/backend/app/scripts/init_super_admin.py) script |

