## 🚀 Tech Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 16, React, TypeScript, Zustand, Framer Motion |
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python), Uvicorn, SlowAPI |
| **Database** | Firebase Firestore (NoSQL, real-time) |
| **AI/Embeddings** | FAISS (local vector search), sentence-transformers |
| **LLM Fallback** | Google Gemini AI |
| **Authentication** | JWT (jose), bcrypt |
| **Email** | Gmail SMTP (OTP delivery) |
| **Infrastructure** | Google Cloud Run (containerized, auto-scaling) |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub → `gcloud run deploy --source .` |
| **Security** | CORS, GZip, Rate Limiting, Security Headers middleware |

