## 📈 Scalability Design

- **Multi-university SaaS**: Each university is completely isolated by `university_id`
- **New universities**: Created from Admin Dashboard instantly — no code changes
- **New CMS sections**: Added at runtime — schema is fully dynamic
- **Auto-scaling**: Cloud Run scales to zero (cost-efficient) and up to handle traffic
- **FAISS index**: Rebuilt per-university on first query, cached in memory for speed
- **TTL caching**: University list cached 2 minutes, avoiding cold Firestore reads
- **Semantic caching**: Similar queries return cached AI responses (cost + speed)

